1
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:09,884
小子！
(LORD UHTRED) Boy!

2
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:12,771
潮水要转了!
The tide is on the turn!

3
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,164
我不会再警告你第二次!
I'm not warning you again!

4
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:20,803
船!在那儿!
(OSBERT) Ships! There!

5
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:29,444
丹麦人
Danes.

6
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,284
魔鬼的走狗
The devil's turds.

7
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:34,887
- 他们是商人吗? - 不,他们是来劫掠的维京人!
- Are they traders? - No. They come as Vikings!

8
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,883
走!
We go!

9
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:40,884
走!走!
Go! Go!

10
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:03,169
抓紧!
(MAN) Hold on!

11
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,647


12
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,285


13
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,729
我儿子在哪?
(LORD UHTRED) Where's my son?

14
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:33,282
乌特雷德,带六个人骑马去河边
Uhtred. Take half a dozen men, ride to the river.

15
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:36,011
那里有异教徒,盯着他们，看清楚有多少人
There are pagans there. Watch them, see how many.

16
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,889
- 明白 - 不要多生事端
- Of course. - Do nothing more.

17
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:40,168
是,父亲
(UHTRED) Yes, Father. (GLENNA) Osbert.

18
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:42,482
- 怎么了? - 有船，我看见了
- What is it? - Ships. I saw them.

19
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:45,610
- 什么船? - 丹麦人，正朝河这边来
- What ships? - Danes. They're heading for the river.

20
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,131


21
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,851
愿天主与众圣人保佑我们,他们没有灵魂
God and his saints preserve us. They have no soul.

22
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,843
- 我们该祈祷 - 我们该行动
- We must pray. - We must act.

23
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,606
乌特雷德，不许和他们交战，一个都不行
Uhtred. Do not fight them, not a single one.

24
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,285
- 天黑前回来 - 是
- Be back by nightfall. - Yes.

25
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,920
他们是天主降下的惩罚,为了我们的罪孽
They are sent by God to punish us for our sins.

26
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:01,811
他们是来支援约克的维京军队的
They're here to support the Viking army in Eofervvic.

27
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:04,440
让神父去祈祷，求天主救我们
Instruct the priest to pray for our deliverance.

28
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,284
- 埃尔弗里克！ - 大人？
- Aelfric! - Lord?

29
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:09,603
- 把他们带进去 - 把妇女和老人带进来
- Get them inside. - Take in the women and elders.

30
00:02:09,760 --> 00:02:11,842
其余人去高地，别让人看见
The rest to higher ground, out of sight.

31
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,765
召集乡民，我要这座要塞里的每一个男人
Rouse the country. I want every man in this fortress.

32
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,287
每个人都要做好赴死的准备
And every man must be prepared to die.

33
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,404
左舷准备划桨！
(MAN 1) Port side ready to row!

34
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:26,245
左舷就位！右舷准备划桨！
(MAN 2) Port side ready! (MAN 1) Starboard side ready to row!

35
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,050
右舷准备划桨！
(MAN 2) Starboard side ready to row!

36
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,324
父亲
Father.

37
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,601
收桨！收桨！
(MAN 1) Rest your oars! (MAN 2) Rest your oars!

38
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,369
尝尝
Taste.

39
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:47,769
没味道，是淡水
Bland. Fresh.

40
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,002
- 甜水 - 对
- Sweetwater. - Yes.

41
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:52,322
你还看到了什么？
What else do you see?

42
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,169
我看到一条清澈的河
EARL RAGNAR: I see a clear river,

43
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,810
鱼大得像人的腿一样粗
fish as big as a man's leg.

44
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:59,208
我看到树林里到处是猎物
I see a forest alive with meat.

45
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,966
不止如此，我看到了一个可以安享晚年的地方
More than that, I see a place to grow fat and old.

46
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,690


47
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,929
有马
Horses.

48
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:09,126
是啊，我还看到了探子
Yeah. And I see spies,

49
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,770
吓得裤裆都湿了
shitting themselves.

50
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:14,965


51
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,443
我们以剑迎剑！
We'll meet sword with sword!

52
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:24,405
你们是异教徒！
You are pagans!

53
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,562
我们有更伟大的天主站在我们这边！
We have the greater God on our side!

54
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,849
基尔坦，我觉得该给这小子一个教训
Kjartan. I think we should teach this boy a lesson.

55
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,445
靠进去
(KJARTAN) Taking her in.

56
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,967
- 快跑！- 加快速度！
- At speed! - (MAN) Pick up the speed!

57
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,731


58
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:43,242


59
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:48,484
跟我回去！快走！去要塞！快跟上！
(MAN 1) Come back with me! Move it! (MAN 2) To the fort! Come on!

60
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:52,046
带上孩子！快走！
(MAN 3) Grab the children! Move!

61
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,806
你想问我为什么不守护村子
(LORD UHTRED) Why do I leave the villages unprotected

62
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,291
而是把人都撤进堡内？
and bring the men inside?

63
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,488
这是你想问的吗？
Is that your question?

64
00:04:58,640 --> 00:05:02,167
村子烧了还能重建，战士死了就是死了
A village can be rebuilt, a warrior can die only once.

65
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,800
丹麦人可能正往南朝约克进发
The Danes may be heading south to Eofervvic,

66
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:08,009
但一路上碰到谁他们都会杀
but they will kill whoever they can on the way.

67
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,809
去把神父找来
Now, go and End the priest.

68
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,803
好的，父亲
(OSBERT) Yes, Father.

69
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,884
进来吧，奥斯伯特，别躲在阴暗处
(BEOCCA) Come in, Osbert, don't skulk in the shadows.

70
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,042
父亲让我来问您准备好了没
(OSBERT) He wants to know if you're ready.

71
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,964
快了
(BEOCCA) Almost.

72
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:30,561
你知道我在忙什么吗？
Do you know what I'm tasked with?

73
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:34,486
- 呃，写信？- 是回信，回的是这封信
- Um, a letter? - A response to a letter, this letter

74
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,404
埃拉国王来的信
from King Aella.

75
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:39,883
他请求你父亲出兵相助
Asking your father for his support, his army,

76
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:43,123
帮他夺回约克城
to help recapture the city of Eofervvic.

77
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,601
这就是为什么读书写字很重要
This is why it's important to read and write.

78
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,250
父亲不识字，也不会写
Father can't read nor write.

79
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,562
唉，你父亲这把年纪，学也学不了了
Yeah, well, for your father it's too late.

80
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:52,121
埃拉国王大可以派个人骑马来传话
King Aella could have sent a man on horseback.

81
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:54,931
骑马送信的人说的就一定是真话吗?
Who's to say the man on horseback speaks the truth?

82
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:57,526
或者他还记得原话吗?
Or has remembered the true message?

83
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:02,205
这些文字记录的是历史，是事实
What these letters will represent is history, facts.

84
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:05,489
你父亲正在通知埃拉国王和奥斯伯特国王
Your father is informing King Aella and King Osbert

85
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:08,883
他将与他们的军队一同在约克会师
he will be alongside their armies at Eoferwic.

86
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:12,726
贝班堡的印章便是这封信真实性的保证
And the mark of Bebbanburg will guarantee the truth of it.

87
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:14,484
我们为什么要为约克而战?
Why do we fight for Eofervvic?

88
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,483
我们为约克而战
Well, we fight for Eofervvic

89
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:20,964
是因为我们不想眼睁睁看着英格兰一块一块地落入丹麦人之地
because we do not wish to see England, piece by piece, become Daneland.

90
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:24,727
哈哈,我听说我们曾经也是异教徒
Heh, heh. I heard it said that we were pagans once,

91
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:27,611
说沃登和奥丁其实是同一个神
that Woden and Odin are the same.

92
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:30,081
我们认清了自己的错误,转而皈依罗马
We saw the error of our ways, looked to Rome.

93
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,641
我听说异教徒有凶猛的战争之神
I heard the pagans had fierce gods of war.

94
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,962
我们走的是正道,他们才是走错了路
Well, we are right and they are mistaken.

95
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:37,282
奥斯伯特,我们是蒙受祝福的人
Osbert, we are blessed.

96
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,761
我得让你对着圣卡斯伯特的梳子发誓
I should make you swear on St Cuthbert's comb

97
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:42,082
以后再也不许提沃登之类的名字
never to mention the likes of Woden again.

98
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,925
可要是我有一条狗叫沃登呢?
But what if I had a hound called Woden?

99
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:48,687
- 那你怎么办? - 要是你有头猪叫托尔呢?
- What would you do then? - What if you had a pig called Thor?

100
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:51,650
- 走吧，去见你父亲 - 一头叫托尔的猪
- Come. Let's go see your father. - A pig called Thor.

101
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:55,725
- 那真的是圣卡斯伯特的梳子吗? - 当然是圣卡斯伯特的梳子
- Is it really St Cuthbert's comb? - Of course it's St Cuthbert's comb,

102
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:58,724
他的圣发就留在那梳齿之间
and his holy hair lies in the teeth of that comb.

103
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:02,362
-你父亲人呢？- 他在跟侍女鬼混
- Where was your father last? - He was humping the servant girl.

104
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,170
- 胡说，奥斯伯特 - 我没胡说
- That's a lie,，Osbert. - No.

105
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:07,642
- 你就没打算消停吗? - 没有
- Are you never gonna tire of teasing? - Nope.

106
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:10,371
有骑兵来了!
(MAN) Horsemen approaching!

107
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:30,121
他骑的是乌特雷德的马
He rides Uhtred's horse.

108
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,091
奥斯伯特
(BEOCCA) Osbert.

109
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:58,210
不，不!
No. No!

110
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,651


111
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,441
把他剩下的身体埋了
Bury what's left of him.

112
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,763
奥斯伯特，走吧
(BEOCCA) Osbert, come on.

113
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:28,521
提醒我，我最后跟他说了什么
Remind me of the last words I spoke to him.

114
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:31,411
你让他只看，不许出战，我们...
You told him to watch and do not Tight. We have...

115
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,324
不许出战就是不许出战
Do not fight means do not fight.

116
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:36,211
- 他还年轻 - 到约克之前不许出战
- He was young. (LORD UHTRED) No fight until Eoferwic.

117
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,931
您要见奥斯伯特，大人
(BEOCCA) You wanted to see Osbert, my lord.

118
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,970
你
You.

119
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,485
你现在叫乌特雷德
You are now called Uhtred.

120
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:45,450
乌特雷德，乌特雷德之子，你带着那块石头了吗，那块琥珀?
Uhtred, son of Uhtred. You have your stone, the amber?

121
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,967
- 带了 - 神父会带你了解你的历史
- Yes. - The priest will show you your history,

122
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:50,686
- 那些羊皮卷，让他明白 - 大人，我...
- parchments. Make him understand. (BEOCCA) Lord, I...

123
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,842
我想再给他施一次洗礼
I should like to baptise him again.

124
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,162
若他以乌特雷德之名到达天堂之门
If he arrives at heaven's gate as Uhtred,

125
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:57,846
他们可能会纳闷奥斯伯特去哪儿了
they might wonder what's happened to Osbert.

126
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,287
你必须做的就做，但也照我说的办
Do what you must, but do as I ask.

127
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,930
遵命，大人
(BEOCCA) Lord.

128
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:06,526
孩子，我们曾经是这里的王，统治着
We were kings here once, boy. Kings of all the lands

129
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:09,809
- 图耶德河与泰恩河之间的所有土地 - 我们理应再度称王
- between rivers Tuede and Tine. - We should be kings again.

130
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:13,806
理应如此，但他们称我们什么不重要，只要他们服从就行
We should, but it does not matte,what they call us so long as they obey.

131
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:16,611
我们的祖先打下了这片土地
Our ancestors took this land.

132
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:19,206
这片土地是我们用血肉打下来的
It's been strengthened with our blood and bone.

133
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:23,251
你现在是贝班堡新的继承人，听到了吗？
And now you are the new heir of Bebbanburg. You hear me?

134
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,209
必要时，你要为它而死
And you will die for it if needed.

135
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:28,284
我会把杀了乌特雷德那个人的脑袋交给你
And I'll give you the head of the man who killed Uhtred.

136
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,124
不，你就是乌特雷德！
No, you are Uhtred!

137
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:32,248
你没在听我说话吗？
Have you not been listening to me?

138
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:35,802
别跟我说你要干什么，你还只是个毛头小子
Do not tell me what it is you will do, you are just a pup.

139
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:40,409
你什么都不用给我，你只要看，只要学
You will give me nothing. You will watch and you will learn.

140
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:45,686
在他母亲念叨我之前让他接受洗礼吧
Put him in the water before his mother's tongue gives me grief.

141
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,808
她不是我母亲
She's not my mother.

142
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:52,644
你会带他上战场去看去学吗？
Will you take him with you to battle to watch and learn?

143
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,963
我要你挑三十个人，留守贝班堡
I need you to choose 30 men and remain here at Bebbanburg.

144
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:58,851
保护这孩子，他是继承人
Protect the boy. He is the heir.

145
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,965
三十人守得住，粮食也够用，帮我做这件事？
Thirty will hold, few enough to feed. Do this for me?

146
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,566
我更想跟你一起去，但我会照你说的做
I'd rather be with you, but I'll do as you ask.

147
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,051
谢了
Thank you.

148
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,444
来，快点
(GLENNA) Come on, quickly.

149
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,523
上去，快走
Up there, go on.

150
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,563
快，快些
(BEOCCA) Hurry, please.

151
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,967


152
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,321
天父啊
(BEOCCA) Heavenly Father,

153
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:32,563
请接纳你的仆人乌特雷德
receive your servant, Uhtred,

154
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:35,530
让他进入圣徒的神圣国度
into the holy kind of saints

155
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:39,207
与最光明的天使同列
and into the ranks of the most bright angels.

156
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,850
愿你的圣水洗净他
Let your holy waters cleanse him

157
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:46,209
使他配得上你的祝福
and make and him worthy of your blessing,

158
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:50,604
让他成为你的器皿与权杖
make him your instrument and your rod.

159
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:56,602
让他领悟文字的力量
Let him realise the significance of the written word

160
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:59,240
好让他了解你的荣耀
so that he may learn of your glory

161
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:02,888
进而传播你的福音
and in turn may spread your word.

162
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:07,009
- 贝奥... - 让他在智慧中成长
- Beo.._ - Let him grow in wisdom

163
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:08,810
在敬畏中成长
and in respect

164
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:11,767
- 好让他以虔敬之道领导众人 - 贝奥...
- so he may lead in a godly manner. - Beo...

165
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,331
贝奥卡，他已受洗净了
Beocca, he's cleansed.

166
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,088
- 阿门
- Amen. 

167
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:21,770
乌特雷德，贝班堡的乌特雷德之子，欢迎来到基督的世界
Uhtred, son of Uhtred of Bebbanburg, welcome to the Christian world.

168
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:25,328
看看你的子民和你的土地
Behold your people and your land.

169
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:28,847

170
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:57,042


171
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,442
人都去哪了，士兵们呢?
(UHTRED) Where are the people, the soldiers?

172
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,887
在去约克的路上，你父亲带领着他们
On the road to Eofervvic, led by your father,

173
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:13,361
去与另外两位国王会合
where they'll join the other two kings.

174
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,966
- 没带我? - 你要留在贝班堡
- Without me? - You are to remain at Bebbanburg

175
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:19,966
跟你叔父待在这儿，我负责保护你，要是想打架，就来跟我掰手腕
with your uncle. I'm to keep you safe. You wish to fight, we arm-wrestle.

176
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:22,964
- 神父呢? - 跟你父亲去了，吃东西吧
- Where's the priest? - With your father. Eat.

177
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:25,964
你要去马厩干活，乌特雷德
You have work to do, Uhtred, in the stables.

178
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:28,805
好在他们还给我们留了几匹马
Thankfully, we've been left some horses.

179
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:31,649
- 你该吃点东西 - 我不饿
- You should eat. - (UHTRED) I'm not hungry.

180
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,165
我们有活要干
(AELFRIC) We have work to do.

181
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,049
马粪要铲
Horse shit to shovel.

182
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:37,646
干完了来找我
Come and find me when you've finished.

183
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,684
斯卡利昂,
Scallion,

184
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:26,688
我兄弟如果战死，那孩子也必须死
if my brother falls in battle, the boy must fall.

185
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:02,248


186
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,962


187
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:08,489
走这么远，连个接风的人都没有
(EARL RAGNAR) All this way and no reception party.

188
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:10,529
拉格纳伯爵
(GUTHRUM) Earl Ragnar.

189
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:12,643
古斯鲁姆
(EARL RAGNAR) Guthrum.

190
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:15,691
- 你还好吗? - 好，就是饿了
- How are you? - I'm fine. I'm hungry.

191
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,365
- 你的孩子呢? - 快来了
- (GUTHRUM) And your boy? - He's coming.

192
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:19,443
拉格纳，我带来了人马
(UBBA) Ragnar. (EARL RAGNAR) I brought men, horses.

193
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,841
见到你真好，一切都好?
Good to see you. You well?

194
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:24,566


195
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:26,688
你把他儿子的头颅当礼物送给他?
You made a gift of his own son's head?

196
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,930
那位领主是什么反应?
How did this lord react?

197
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,411
他什么都没做
He did nothing.

198
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:34,690
他把手下的战士带进城堡,，待在里头不出来
He brought his warriors into the fortress, kept them inside.

199
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:37,925
- 那不是胆怯 - 是隐忍
- It was not cowardice. - (GUTHRUM) Restraint.

200
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,931
他在保存实力
He is saving his men.

201
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,730
此人就是乌特雷德
(UBBA) That man is Uhtred.

202
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:43,848
诺森布里亚三位国王之一
One of the three kings of Northumbria.

203
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,968
- 骁勇的战士国王 - 另外两个都是蠢货
- Warrior king. - (GUTHRUM) Other two are fools.

204
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:48,521
只顾着内斗
They'd rather be fighting each other.

205
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:51,445
- 此话当真? - 埃拉王和奥斯伯特王,
- This is true? - King Aella and King Osbert,

206
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:55,400
两人都争着要占约克
they both lay claim to Eofervvic.

207
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:58,564
- 他们的名字真是奇怪 
- They have the strangest of names. - (CHUCKLES)

208
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:01,530
- 那我们什么时候开打? - 快了，但愿如此
- So when do we fight? - Soon, I hope.

209
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,924
我还没决定
I'm still to decide.

210
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:13,721
不管蠢不蠢，他们有三支军队
Fools or not, they have three armies.

211
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:17,804
- 他们确实人多 - 但各自为战
- They have numbers. - (EARL RAGNAR) But are divided.

212
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:21,806
三个国王，却只有一个能统领全局的人，就是这个乌特雷德
Three kings, but only one who can lead them. This Uhtred.

213
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:26,010
杀了他，整个诺森布里亚就是我们的
Kill him and Northumbria is ours, all of it.

214
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:28,009

215
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:31,130
听他说，听这小子说，他让我想起了年轻时的自己
Listen to him. Listen to the boy. He reminds me of me.

216
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:33,601
对，你年轻的时候，哈哈
Yeah, when you were younger. Heh, heh.

217
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,285
当然是年轻的时候
Of course when I was younger.

218
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:37,249
- 他不过是个孩子 - 随便说说
- He's just a boy. - Just saying.

219
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:40,085
- 乌巴… - 你是说我老了？斯托里
- (EARL RAGNAR) Ubba... - Did you say I was old? Storri.

220
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,685
- 没有 - 我没有老
- No. - (UBBA) I'm not getting old.

221
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,330
乌巴
Ubba.

222
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:45,761
我已经看过城外的地形了
I have seen the land outside the city.

223
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:48,491
我心里有个计划，是个好计划
I have a plan in mind, a good plan.

224
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:52,250
我儿子也想跟你们一起见见血
And my son would like to wet his sword with you.

225
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:54,562
那我们打不打？
So do we fight?

226
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:59,449
斯托里？
Storri?

227
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:03,411
征兆不错，就在今晨，我看见一只渡鸦
The signs are good. Only this morning, I saw a raven

228
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:06,803
朝撒克逊人的营地飞去，像是在召唤我跟上
fly towards the Saxon camp, and it was asking me to follow.

229
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,849
- 我确信如此 - 嗯
- I'm sure of it. - Mm.

230
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,688
- 那就开打 -
- Then we fight. 

231
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:19,002
开打！
(MAN) We fight!

232
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,850


233
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:44,170
这是什么鬼地方？
(KING OSBERT) What kind of hell is this?

234
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,970
这是异教徒的地狱
(AELLA) it's a pagan's hell.

235
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,690
我们人数占优
We outnumber them.

236
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,842
还有更多人，一定有
There are more. There must be.

237
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,606
计划不变，先派一半人马出击
Nothing changes. We attack with half our number,

238
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:55,650
摸清他们的底细后，另一半跟进
second half to follow once we have the measure of them.

239
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:58,531
- 他们已经放弃了高地 - 埃拉王
- They have conceded higher ground. - (KING OSBERT) King Aella,

240
00:16:58,680 --> 00:17:01,843
你和乌特雷德大人的军队率先发起冲锋
yours and Lord Uhtred's armies will attack in the first wave.

241
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:04,401
预备！预备！
(AELLA) Prepare! Prepare!

242
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,211


243
00:17:06,360 --> 00:17:07,850
举盾!
Shield!

244
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:11,684
不，不，别撇下我
No. No, not without me.

245
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:37,765
天黑之前，我们就能扫清这帮瘟神,
Come nightfall, we'll be rid of this plague

246
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:40,890
然后清点我们该得的战利品!
and counting our share of the plunder!

247
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:42,371

248
00:17:46,360 --> 00:17:48,169
我的盾牌
(AELLA) My shield.

249
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:50,967


250
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:55,882


251
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:02,771


252
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:13,330


253
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:00,209
杀光他们!
Kill them all!

254
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:03,807


255
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,962


256
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:22,363
盾墙撑住了
(AELLA) The wall is holding.

257
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:26,726
上！手压在盾牌下面，往前顶！顶！
(LORD UHTRED) Go! Hands below your shield and drive! Drive!

258
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,650
后退!
Ease.

259
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:32,848
后退!
(MAN) Ease!

260
00:19:34,600 --> 00:19:36,489
后退!
Ease!

261
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:39,727
- 后退! - 前进!
- Ease! - (LORD UHTRED) Push!

262
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:42,201
继续前进！起效了!
Keep pushing! it's working!

263
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:52,411
把他们压垮!
Drive them!

264
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:54,171


265
00:19:58,720 --> 00:20:01,530
他们撑不住了，还不了手，我们赢了，你看
They're tiring, can't fight back. We're winning, look.

266
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,011
我们赢了
(MAN) We're winning.

267
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,521
- 跟上! -
- Follow! - (MEN SHOUTING)

268
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:09,371


269
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:12,281
往前冲!
Drive on!

270
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:17,600
还不行! 还不行!
Not yet! Not yet!

271
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,005
天主啊，不
Dear God, no.

272
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:41,964
立盾墙!
Shield!

273
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:43,849

Wall!

274
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:47,326
仁慈无边的天主啊，不要让这一切发生
Dear God of infinite mercy, not this.

275
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,044
杀光他们!
Kill them all!

276
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:58,364


277
00:21:01,520 --> 00:21:03,363


278
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:06,444
护腿! 护腿!
(LORD UHTRED) Legs! Legs!

279
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:08,011
保护你们的腿!
Protect your legs!

280
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:11,529
举起你的利剑
Lift up your sword

281
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:14,763
庇护这些以你之名浴血的英格兰战士
and spare these men of England who fight in your name.

282
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:19,563
让那些异教徒的心胆俱裂, 魂飞魄散
Let the heathens' hearts crumble and wither.

283
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:23,441
将你的神力赐予这些英格兰战士
Bestow your power upon these men of England,

284
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:27,002
让他们用恶鬼的血来荣耀你的圣名
so they can glorify your name with the blood of the devils.

285
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:29,891
此刻请垂怜我们，主啊
Have mercy now, Lord.

286
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:34,371
不要抛弃我们，不要抛弃英格兰
Do not forsake us. Do not forsake England.

287
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:46,640
跟我来! 跟我来!
(LORD UHTRED) Follow me! Follow me!

288
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:49,369
拿下他!
Take him!

289
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:53,691


290
00:21:53,840 --> 00:21:57,925
收紧盾墙！收紧盾墙，拿下他！
(EARL RAGNAR) Close the shield wall! Close the wall and take him!

291
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,923
啊！
Unh! Unh.

292
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,130
不
No.

293
00:22:12,120 --> 00:22:15,363


294
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,722
这小子像只黄蜂，哈哈
He's like a wasp. Ha, ha.

295
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:23,362


296
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:27,611


297
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:31,531
-可惜黄蜂没了刺  - 是啊
(EARL RAGNAR) Wasp has lost its sting. (RAGNAR) Yeah.

298
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,451


299
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,290


300
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:41,442


301
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:44,331
你确定他是撒克逊人？他打起来像个丹麦人
(RAGNAR) Are you sure he's a Saxon? He fights like a Dane.

302
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:46,005
是啊
(EARL RAGNAR) Yeah.

303
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,009


304
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:57,489


305
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:01,289


306
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,805


307
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:07,925


308
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:11,091
起来！
(MAN 2) Get up!

309
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:15,446


310
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:18,883

311
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:23,404


312
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,725


313
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:32,804
- 放开她
- (BRIDA SCREAMING) - (EARL RAGNAR) Leave her.

314
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,250
她得活着
She is to live.

315
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:40,444
这些年轻的，留着有用
Some of these young ones can come in useful.

316
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:45,969
父亲，这就是我跟你提过的那个男孩
Father, here's the boy I spoke of.

317
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:50,330
差点要了你命的那个？你就把他扔给我？
The one who almost killed you? You're leaving him with me?

318
00:23:50,480 --> 00:23:53,723
我还从没见过谁能在你手里占到便宜
I've never seen a man get the better of you yet.

319
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:57,370

320
00:23:58,160 --> 00:24:00,811


321
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:11,804
给我切点鸡肉
(RAVN) Cut me some chicken.

322
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:21,290
小心,刀刃很锋利
Careful, the blade is sharp.

323
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:23,761
能要人命的
It can kill a man.

324
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:33,171
鸡肉在你盘子里了
The chicken is on your platter.

325
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:42,050
你一直是瞎子吗?
Have you always been blind?

326
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:44,203
哦，我能看到不少
Oh, I see enough.

327
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:49,847
他们在下面杀的是什么人?
So who have they been killing below?

328
00:24:51,080 --> 00:24:52,411
俘虏
(UHTRED) Prisoners.

329
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:57,568
刚才杀了个国王
Just now a king.

330
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:59,927
他死得英勇吗?
Did he die well?

331
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:03,086
- 没有 - 那他本就不配当国王
- No. - Then he shouldn't have been king.

332
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:05,601


333
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:10,806
告诉我,大厅正中坐的是谁?
Tell me, who sits in the middle of the hall?

334
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,491


335
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:13,641


336
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:18,480
是一个大块头和一个小个子吗?
Is it the big man and a small man?

337
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:23,406
是的，他们中间还坐着一个灰发男人
(UHTRED) Yes, and a grey man sits in between them.

338
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:28,009
如果你能活下去，就得提防那个大块头——乌巴
If you get to live, you should beware of the big man. Ubba.

339
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:33,406
我的忠告是，永远别惹乌巴
My advice for you is to never cross Ubba

340
00:25:33,560 --> 00:25:36,131
而且永远，永远别跟他动手
and never, never fight him.

341
00:25:36,280 --> 00:25:40,205
- 如果我能活下去? - 他只听众神的话
- If I get to live? - He listens to no one but the gods.

342
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:46,049
听命于众神的人，谁都摸不透他
Men who take their orders from the gods are unpredictable.

343
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,690
你说'如果我能活下去'
What did you mean

344
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:52,649
是什么意思?
when you said if I get to live?

345
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:54,484
你是我的俘虏
You're my prisoner.

346
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:59,049
那个灰发男人应该是埃格伯特
The grey man will be Egbert.

347
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:01,043
他是个撒克逊郡长
He's a Saxon ealdorman.

348
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:06,206
他已宣誓效忠，如今自称国王
He has pledged allegiance and now calls himself king.

349
00:26:06,360 --> 00:26:08,966
他不过是个傀儡国王
He is king of nothing.

350
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:13,728
用不了多久，英格兰所有国王都将是傀儡国王
Soon all of the kings in England shall be kings of nothing.

351
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:16,486
诺森布里亚已归我们所有
Northumbria is ours.

352
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:18,483
麦西亚也快了
Mercia will soon by ours.

353
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:21,405
然后是东盎格利亚、康沃卢姆
Then East Anglia, Cornwalum,

354
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:27,488
以及最丰厚的奖励，就是威塞克斯，最后的王国
and then the greatest prize is the last kingdom, Wessex.

355
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,130
我听说过威塞克斯
I've heard of Wessex.

356
00:26:29,280 --> 00:26:32,011
任何东西都能在威塞克斯的土地上生长
Anything will grow in Wessex.

357
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:34,162


358
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,324
告诉我你叫什么
(RAVN) Tell me your name.

359
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,050
乌特雷德
Uhtred.

360
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:40,202
我是贝班堡的郡长
I'm the ealdorman of Bebbanburg.

361
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:43,762
- 是吗? - 是的，我在北边有封地
- You are, huh? - I am. I own lands to the north.

362
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:47,527
你当这片土地的郡长多久了?
How long have you been an ealdorman of these lands?

363
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:57,610
你父亲选择跟我们开战
Your father chose to fight us

364
00:26:57,760 --> 00:27:00,650
现在已经死了
and is now dead.

365
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:07,002
他……他不喜欢我
He... He was not fond of me.

366
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,850


367
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:17,847
我现在明白了，为什么我儿子要留你一命
I now understand why my son spared you,

368
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:21,120
贝班堡的乌特雷德
Uhtred of Bebbanburg.

369
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:23,601
你是个战士
You are a warrior.

370
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:28,243
来，喝点麦酒
Have some ale.

371
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,809
喝吧
Drink it.

372
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:37,003
多喝点
Lots of it.

373
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:14,651
拿去
Here.

374
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,205
搬上去
Take it up there.

375
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:20,051


376
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:29,128
我想把他们两个都留下，男孩和女孩
I'm thinking of keeping them both, the boy and the girl.

377
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:31,248
可以帮你母亲干活
Can help your mother.

378
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:35,809
- 有意见? - 没有
- Disagree? - No.

379
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,801
但我们毕竟杀了他父亲
But we did kill his father.

380
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:41,811
如果他是郡长，我们可以拿他换赎金
If he's an ealdorman, we could sell him for ransom.

381
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:43,803
也许吧
Perhaps.

382
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:51,964
布丽达，小心别把水洒了，地板会变成烂泥的
Brida, be careful not to spill the water. You'll turn the floor to mud.

383
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:54,282
乌特雷德，去劈柴
Uhtred, wood needs to be chopped.

384
00:29:56,280 --> 00:29:58,203
布丽达，你去喂山羊
Brida, you can do the goats.

385
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:01,251
乌特雷德会有时间玩吗?
(THYRA) Will there be time for Uhtred to play?

386
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,562
干完活才能玩
Only when work is done.

387
00:30:06,080 --> 00:30:08,924
我不喜欢咱们女儿跟奴隶一起玩
I don't like our daughter having to play with slaves.

388
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:12,209
- 他们只是孩子 - 各有各的位置
- They're only children. - They have a place.

389
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:13,930
暴脾气
Grumpy.

390
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:21,289
牵我的马来
(RAGNAR) My horse.

391
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:24,125
嘿, 拉格纳·拉格纳松
Hey, Ragnar Ragnarson.

392
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:26,851
嘿, 不知道哪儿来的乌特雷德
(RAGNAR) Hey, Uhtred of wherever.

393
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:29,162
你能教我用剑吗?
How about you teach me how to use a sword?

394
00:30:29,320 --> 00:30:31,322
我们不教奴隶如何战斗
We don't teach slaves how to fight.

395
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:34,006
你那张嘴迟早会要了你的命，小子
That tongue of yours will be your death, boy.

396
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:36,242
现在，给我回去干活
Now, get back to work.

397
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:41,285
你们打算怎么玩?
What does the play involve?

398
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:43,363
我们在峡谷里建了一座大厅
We built a hall in the gorge.

399
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:45,727
我是女主人，乌特雷德是战士
I'm the mistress and Uhtred is a warrior.

400
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,291
不是仆人?
Not a servant?

401
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:49,488
这是个游戏
It is a game.

402
00:30:50,800 --> 00:30:53,007


403
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,491
- 狼来了  - 乌特雷德
- A wolf! - Uhtred.

404
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,051
就是一头狼
(UHTRED) That's it, a wolf.

405
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:58,123
野猪，小心!
(BRIDA) Boar. Watch out!

406
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:00,521
我看见了，尖牙利齿，黄眼睛
(UHTRED) I saw it. Its sharp teeth and yellow eyes.

407
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:04,605
- 别让狼靠近我，乌特雷德 - 用火把它们赶走
- Don't let the wolves get to me, Uhtred. - Use the Ere to keep them away.

408
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:07,843
我看见它们了，跟乌巴一样壮，味道比他还难闻
I see them. They're as big as Ubba and smell worse.

409
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,764

410
00:31:12,320 --> 00:31:13,765
你看见了吗?
Did you see that?

411
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,651


412
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,771
乌特雷德
Uhtred.

413
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:21,729
待在上面
Stay up there.

414
00:31:22,320 --> 00:31:24,084
你看
Look.

415
00:31:24,560 --> 00:31:27,803
乌特雷德，出什么事了? 待在上面，蒂拉
(THYRA) Uhtred, what is happening? (UHTRED) Stay up there, Thyra.

416
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:30,406
- 是斯文，他不会伤害你的 - 但他会杀了我们
- It's Sven, he won't hurt you. - (BRIDA) But he'll kill us.

417
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,289


418
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:34,283
他要杀我们! 快跑!
(BRIDA) He'll kill us! Run!

419
00:31:41,720 --> 00:31:43,643
那是一把真剑
That was a real sword.

420
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,450
我看见了
(BRIDA) l saw it.

421
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:47,602
- 啊! 乌特雷德! - 蒂拉
- (THYRA) Ah! Uhtred! - Thyra.

422
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:49,762
乌特雷德!
(THYRA) umred!

423
00:31:59,840 --> 00:32:01,205


424
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:07,284

425
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,364
脸怎么了？
(RAGNAR) whats this?

426
00:32:13,560 --> 00:32:15,767
你又打架了?
You been fighting again?

427
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:18,567
- 是的 - 跟斯文打的?
- (UHTRED) Yes. - With Sven?

428
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:22,165
- 基尔坦的儿子? - 是的
- Kjartan's son? - (UHTRED) Yes.

429
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:25,731
- 乌特雷德，他比你大多了 - 他是个烂人
- Uhtred, he's much bigger than you. - He's a turd.

430
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,451
你干嘛这么说? 谁先动手的?
(SIGRID) Why do you say that? (RAVN) Who started it?

431
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:32,371
- 谁先动的手? - 是我先动的手
- Who began the fight? - (UHTRED) I began the fight.

432
00:32:32,520 --> 00:32:34,727
就因为他是个烂人?
For no other reason than that he's a turd?

433
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:37,763
丹麦人为更小的事就杀人了
Danes have murdered for less.

434
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:39,809
乌特雷德，够了
(SIGRID) Uhtred, that's enough.

435
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:42,881
- 你想被卖掉吗，小子? - 我想吃饭
- You want to be sold, boy? - I wish to eat.

436
00:32:43,040 --> 00:32:44,804
- 大声说 - 我想吃饭
- Speak up. - (UHTRED) I wish to eat.

437
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:46,849
你想吃饭?
You want to eat?

438
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:51,248
你想吃饭?
You want to eat?

439
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:53,004
你知道吗
You know what?

440
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:55,003
要我说你就该饿着
I say you starve.

441
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:57,891
打架可以理解，不听话可不行
Fighting is expected, disobedience is not.

442
00:32:58,040 --> 00:33:00,850
是斯文先动的手
- (SLAP AND UHTRED GRUNTS) -Sven began the fight.

443
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,968
基尔坦!
Kjartan!

444
00:33:04,280 --> 00:33:06,203
基尔坦!
Kjartan!

445
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:14,486
拉格纳伯爵，请先听我说，他是个好孩子
Earl Ragnar, let me first say, he's a good boy.

446
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:17,928
他带着剑闯进我的地盘，我会跟他好好谈谈
He brought a sword onto my land. I will have words with him.

447
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:21,129
- 将来他会在你的船上效力 - 他冒犯了我
- In time, he'll serve on your ship. - He has offended me.

448
00:33:21,280 --> 00:33:24,363
- 他会尊敬你的，他没有恶意 - 他没有恶意?
- He will honour you. He meant no harm. - He meant no harm?

449
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:26,443
他看了我女儿的裸体
He looked at my daughter's nakedness.

450
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:29,080
他受到惩罚了，你那撒克逊奴隶划伤了他
And he was punished. Your Saxon slave cut him.

451
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:31,129
这样我就要放过他吗？
(EARL RAGNAR) Shall I make a square of branches?

452
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:34,887
你是要为你儿子跟我打一架，还是把他叫出来?
Are you gonna fight me for your son or fetch him?

453
00:33:39,800 --> 00:33:43,009
斯文，出来
Sven. Come out here.

454
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:47,881
- 把你要说的话告诉他 - 对不起
- Tell him what you have to say. - I'm sorry.

455
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:51,601
- 他听不到你说话 - 大人，对不起，我不该那样做
- He can't hear you. - I'm sorry, lord, for what I did.

456
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:58,490
你对我女儿动手动脚
You laid hands on my daughter.

457
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:00,371
你扒掉了她的衣服
You stripped her naked.

458
00:34:00,520 --> 00:34:03,410
- 大人，只是脱了一半 - 大人，他这个年纪嘛
- Half-naked, lord. - He's at an age, lord.

459
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,884
是这样吗?
Is this true?

460
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:09,805
- 只脱了一半? - 是的,大人
- Half-naked? - Yes, lord.

461
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:16,965
那我就只挖他一只眼
Then I shall only take his one eye.

462
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:19,043
不要，大人，求你了
(KJARTAN) No, lord, please. (SVEN) Ah!

463
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:23,610
基尔坦，我将你驱逐出我的领地
(EARL RAGNAR) Kjartan, you are banished from my land.

464
00:34:24,680 --> 00:34:28,048

465
00:34:46,040 --> 00:34:48,361
我有样东西给你
I have something for you.

466
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,885
什么东西?
What is it?

467
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:53,964
一块护身符，托尔之锤
An amulet. Thor's hammer.

468
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:56,846
- 可是…… - 可是什么?
- But, uh... - But what?

469
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,923
你是基督徒
You're Christian.

470
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,841
拿着
Take it.

471
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:06,887
- 我不能拿 - 你不想要吗?
- I can't. - Don't you want it?

472
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:08,451
- 我想要 - 那就拿着
- I do want it. - Take it.

473
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:10,602
- 我在想办法拿 - 拿着
- I'm trying. - Take it.

474
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:13,047
- 我觉得他不想要 - 我想要
- (RAGNAR) I don't think he wants it. - I do want it.

475
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:15,646
不，我看不见得
(RAGNAR) No, I don't think so.

476
00:35:19,120 --> 00:35:20,929
谢谢
Thank you.

477
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:25,923
跟我说说丹麦
Tell me about Denmark.

478
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:29,771
你的故乡
Your home.

479
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:32,651
丹麦嘛，能说什么
What can I say about Denmark?

480
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:34,644
潮湿
(RAGNAR) It's wet.

481
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:36,928
又苦寒
And harsh.

482
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:41,770
土地很平而且都是沙子，什么也种不出来
The ground is so flat and sandy, you can't grow a fart.

483
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:44,526
所以我们才来英格兰
Which is why we're here in England.

484
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,891
来扎根生息
To grow.

485
00:35:47,040 --> 00:35:50,681
也是为什么小拉格纳不久后要去爱尔兰
And why young Ragnar will soon be going for Ireland.

486
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,842
你要走了?
(UHTRED) You leave to Tight?

487
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:55,282
为了财富
(RAGNAR) To make my wealth.

488
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:59,964
想要土地和银子，就得自己去抢
If you want land or silver, you have to take it.

489
00:36:03,520 --> 00:36:08,686
今天你让我骄傲，乌特雷德
You made me proud today, Uhtred.

490
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,290
你真的让我骄傲
You made me proud.

491
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:45,851
我不认识你
(AELFRIC) I don't know you.

492
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:48,321
你看着不像信使
You don't have the appearance of a messenger,

493
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:51,962
- 乌巴的贡款也还没到期 - 不是的，大人
- and Ubba's payment's not yet due. - (KJARTAN) No, lord.

494
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,330
我是个船主
I was a ship's master.

495
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:58,007
我没有船, 也不需要船主
Well, I have no ships. I need no ship's master.

496
00:37:02,320 --> 00:37:04,448
我有你想听的消息
I have news that you will want to hear.

497
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:09,324
- 说吧 - 我想要些回报，大人
- Well? - I would want something in return, lord.

498
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:12,447
不是现在，也不是钱
Not now, not coin.

499
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:16,168
但也许我们可以长期互相帮衬
But perhaps we can continue to help each other.

500
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:18,011
也许吧
Perhaps.

501
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:20,288
从这里往南走两天
Two days south of here

502
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:23,330
就到了拉格纳伯爵的地盘，我以前侍奉他
is Earl Ragnar, the man I used to serve

503
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,608
后来他把我驱逐出去
until he banished me.

504
00:37:26,640 --> 00:37:30,281
他有个奴隶，他对这个奴隶很好
He has a slave, treats him well.

505
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:36,601
这个奴隶你有权赎回，如果你想的话
This is a slave you're entitled to buy back if you wish to.

506
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:42,202
- 赎回? - 大人，那是您的侄子乌特雷德
- Buy back? - It's your nephew Uhtred, lord.

507
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:44,211
他还活着
He lives.

508
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:01,362
要是我不想被赎回呢?
(UHTRED) What if I'm against being ransomed?

509
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:07,725
你的家人发现你还活着
Your family has discovered that you're still alive

510
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:10,884
他们想把你接回去
and they wish for you to be returned.

511
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,769
但他们得付钱
But they must pay.

512
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:16,925
- 付钱给拉格纳? - 乌巴要抽走一大半
- Pay Ragnar? - Ubba takes more than half.

513
00:38:17,120 --> 00:38:18,929
这很正常
It's normal.

514
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:25,121
但我已经没有家人了
But I have no family.

515
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:31,085
让他们待在那边，把马拴好
(MAN) Keep them over there, tether the horses.

516
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:38,371
斯卡利昂，就是他
Scallion. Him.

517
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:42,044
乌特雷德
Uhtred.

518
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:43,884
他们待你好吗?
Are they treating you well?

519
00:38:44,040 --> 00:38:46,088
- 有得吃，是的 - 好
- I am fed, yes. - Good.

520
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:48,288
好，那就好
Good, that's all we ask.

521
00:38:49,240 --> 00:38:51,481
你脖子上挂的是什么，某种象征吗？
What is that around your neck, some symbol?

522
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:55,167
- 哦，这个? 他们让我戴的 - 我能看看吗?
- Oh, this? They make me wear it. - May I see it?

523
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:04,520
听着，我得和你说实话
(WHISPERS) Look, I will speak plainly.

524
00:39:04,680 --> 00:39:06,205
你叔父会杀了你的
Your uncle will kill you.

525
00:39:07,160 --> 00:39:09,606
明白吗? 你不能回贝班堡
Right? You cannot go back to Bebbanburg.

526
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:11,171
你必须逃走
You must escape.

527
00:39:12,240 --> 00:39:14,686
他想当郡长，想当国王
He wants to be the ealdorman, wants to be king.

528
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,763
就像那边那个可怜虫埃格伯特一样
Like the pathetic Egbert over there.

529
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:20,481
给丹麦主子当傀儡国王，你该去威塞克斯
A puppet king for his Danish masters. You should go to Wessex.

530
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:24,008
去找真正的国王埃塞尔雷德和他的兄弟阿尔弗雷德王子
Seek out for that real King Aethelred and his brother the Prince Alfred,

531
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,969
他们是好人，虔诚的基督徒
they're good men, good Christian men.

532
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:29,203
你在他耳边说够了没有，神父
(EARL RAGNAR) That's enough whispering in his ear, priest.

533
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,445
- 乌特雷德 - 再多说一个字
- Uhtred. - One more word,

534
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:33,523
我就把你的蛋蛋割下来做成钱袋
I'll have your ball bag for a purse.

535
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:37,446
我在那儿等你 不必了
I'll meet you there. That will not be necessary.

536
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,045
他说什么了?
What did he say?

537
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:43,682
他... 他问你有没有好好待我
He... He asked if you were treating me well.

538
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,450
多少? 三百银币
(AELFRIC) How much? (RAVN) Three hundred.

539
00:40:04,600 --> 00:40:06,090
你这是狮子大开口
(AELFRIC) That is a ridiculous amount.

540
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:08,561
一个孩子怎么可能值三百银币?
How can a boy be worth 300 pieces of silver?

541
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:14,090
因为我说了算，因为他是领主，是郡长
Because I say so, because he is a lord and an ealdorman.

542
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,605
不, 他只是个孩子
No, he is a boy.

543
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:19,207
我才是贝班堡的郡长，我掌着印章和旗帜
I am the ealdorman of Bebbanburg. I carry the seal and banner.

544
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:21,966
那印章是我父亲的，现在是我的
That seal is my father's, which is now mine.

545
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:25,488
给我闭嘴，你不过是待价而沽的货
You be silent. You are for sale, nothing more.

546
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:27,768
- 是赎金，大人 - 我就是这个意思
- For ransom, lord. - That's what I said.

547
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:31,003
各位大人，我已经献出了土地和马匹
My lords, I have given up land, horses.

548
00:40:31,160 --> 00:40:34,243
还提供了大量粮食和我的剑
I've offered a generous supply of food as well as my sword.

549
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:37,802
我只求一个公道的价钱来换回我唯一的侄子
All I ask in return is a fair price for my only nephew.

550
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:40,770
你觉得什么价钱算公道?
(RAVN) What would you say is a fair price?

551
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:44,049
- 我出一百银币 - 两百银币
- I'll offer a hundred pieces of silver. - (RAVN) Two hundred.

552
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:48,489
我的效忠加上一百块银子，这价钱够公道了
My allegiance and 100 pieces is surely a fair price.

553
00:40:48,640 --> 00:40:50,961
不够
(RAVN) It is not.

554
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:55,367
我出一百二十银币买这孩子
I will give 120 pieces of silver for the boy.

555
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:57,807
呵呵呵，不够
(RAVN) Heh, heh, heh. Not enough.

556
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:02,124
好吧
Very well.

557
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:04,880
两百块
Two hundred pieces.

558
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:07,168
我接受你的条件
I agree to your terms.

559
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:11,009


560
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:18,529
这孩子卖给拉格纳伯爵了
The boy is sold to Earl Ragnar.

561
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:20,603
- 什么? - 是赎回, 大人
- What? - (RAVN) Ransomed, lord.

562
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:23,047
我就是这个意思，此事已定
That is what I said. The matter is closed.

563
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:27,128
各位大人，我不远万里赶来，还献上了我的忠诚
My lords, I have come a long way. I have offered my allegiance.

564
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:30,204
所以你才能活到现在
Which is why you're allowed to breathe.

565
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:35,408
如果你有异议, 那就是对我有意见
If you have an argument, it's with me now.

566
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:45,449
事情谈完了的话
If business is done,

567
00:41:45,600 --> 00:41:49,127
- 我们喝酒去 - 埃格伯特王该坐下歇歇了
- we have ale to drink. - (UBBA) And King Egbert needs to sit.

568
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:51,482


569
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:01,482
我不用被赎了吗?
(UHTRED) Am I not for ransom anymore?

570
00:42:01,640 --> 00:42:04,769
你听到乌巴说的了，我把你买下来了
(EARL RAGNAR) You heard Ubba, I bought you.

571
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:09,282
我本来想把你献祭给奥丁
I thought I might sacrifice you to Odin.

572
00:42:10,120 --> 00:42:11,610
你花了多少买我?
You bought me for how much?

573
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:14,650
- 太多了 - 多少叫太多?
- Too much. - How much is too much?

574
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:17,451
我那把剑等重的银子
My sword's weight in silver.

575
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:21,605
我承认我可能是吃亏了，但我们喜欢你，孩子
I agree I may have been robbed, but we like you, boy.

576
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:23,808
我们要留下你
We're going to keep you.

577
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,930
这是说我成丹麦人了?
(UHTRED) Does this mean I'm a Dane?

578
00:42:26,080 --> 00:42:28,731
这是说你是乌特雷德·拉格纳松
It means you're Uhtred Ragnarson.

579
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:31,247
- 你现在是我的儿子了 - 啊!
- You are a son to me now. - Ah!

580
00:43:00,240 --> 00:43:02,720
布丽达，不是那边，把山羊从旁边牵出去
Brida, not that way. Take the goat out the side.

581
00:43:02,880 --> 00:43:04,689
下次，我保证
Next time, I promise.

582
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:08,049
- 母亲，你看 - 真美，真的很美
- Mother, look. - It's beautiful. It really is.

583
00:43:08,560 --> 00:43:10,642
我不敢相信我就要失去你了
I can't believe I'm losing you already.

584
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:13,201
我就住在田地对面
I will be living across the field.

585
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:17,046
他要是待你不好，就穿过那片田走回来
If he doesn't treat you well, come marching back across that field.

586
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:34,169
哦，你看这地方
(UHTRED) Oh, look at this place.

587
00:43:34,640 --> 00:43:39,282
乌特雷德，你喜欢我的婚礼项链吗?
Uhtred, do you like my wedding necklace?

588
00:43:39,520 --> 00:43:41,568
喜欢，很漂亮
I do. Very pretty.

589
00:43:41,720 --> 00:43:45,167
他懂什么项链
(RAVN) He doesn't know anything about necklaces.

590
00:43:46,080 --> 00:43:47,445
还不如来问我
You might as well ask me.

591
00:43:47,600 --> 00:43:50,365
乌特雷德，跟我来，帮我宰山羊
Uhtred, with me. You can help me slaughter the goats.

592
00:43:50,520 --> 00:43:52,443
- 我刚洗完澡 - 哈哈
(UHTRED) I've only just washed. (EARL RAGNAR) Ha, ha.

593
00:43:52,600 --> 00:43:55,171
山羊会高兴的
The goats will be pleased.

594
00:43:59,640 --> 00:44:03,440
在那之后，你可以扫扫地
Later you can sweep the floor. Unh! Ha, ha, ha.

595
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:07,010
挪开
Move over.

596
00:44:09,600 --> 00:44:12,570
找个借口聊聊，仅此而已
This is an excuse to talk, that's all.

597
00:44:12,960 --> 00:44:14,291
蒂拉就要成亲了
With Thyra to be married,

598
00:44:14,440 --> 00:44:16,727
也许是时候让你和布丽达定下来了
maybe it's time you got together with Bride.

599
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:20,123
有些男人，不错的男人，在打听她的事
There are men, good men, asking about her.

600
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:22,487
所以你得想清楚你对她算什么
So you have to decide what you are to her.

601
00:44:22,880 --> 00:44:24,530
- 你们两个到底是什么关系 - 呵呵呵
- What you are to each other. - Heh, heh, heh.

602
00:44:24,680 --> 00:44:26,728
- 布丽达有自己的主意 - 是啊
- Brida has her own mind. - She has.

603
00:44:26,880 --> 00:44:28,962
但我看得出她看你的眼神
But I see the way she looks at you.

604
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:34,169
她今晚在林子里看守炭窑
She's watching the charcoal tonight in the woods.

605
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:36,891
骑我的马去找她
Take my horse and join her.

606
00:44:37,040 --> 00:44:39,805
- 地上还暖着呢 - 哈哈哈
- The earth will be warm. - Heh, heh, heh.

607
00:44:41,240 --> 00:44:42,969
为什么不呢
Why not?

608
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:48,770
我只是以为要成为真正的丹麦人，就得娶个丹麦女人
I just thought in order to be a real Dane, I had to marry a Dane.

609
00:44:51,080 --> 00:44:52,411
去吧
Come on.

610
00:44:53,760 --> 00:44:56,843
我疼你，就像疼小拉格纳一样
I love you like I love young Ragnar.

611
00:45:01,680 --> 00:45:03,045

612
00:45:05,240 --> 00:45:06,924


613
00:45:11,440 --> 00:45:14,205


614
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:30,405
你在这儿干什么
What are you doing here?

615
00:46:06,760 --> 00:46:09,331


616
00:46:12,520 --> 00:46:15,922


617
00:46:24,800 --> 00:46:27,724
你有没有想过你以前作为英格兰人的日子
Do you ever think of your English life?

618
00:46:30,960 --> 00:46:33,884
在我们来到拉格纳这里之前，你是什么样的人
Who you were before we came to Ragnar?

619
00:46:36,280 --> 00:46:37,805
没有
No.

620
00:46:39,640 --> 00:46:41,244
你呢
Do you?

621
00:46:45,400 --> 00:46:47,004
- 我想到我… - 嘘
- I think of who I... - Shh.

622
00:46:47,160 --> 00:46:48,924


623
00:46:50,520 --> 00:46:52,329
有声音
(BRIDA) Voices.

624
00:46:54,160 --> 00:46:56,128
下面有人
Men below.

625
00:47:02,840 --> 00:47:04,410


626
00:47:11,680 --> 00:47:14,445
是丹麦人，他们是谁
Danes. Who are they?

627
00:47:15,800 --> 00:47:17,848
那是基尔坦
That's Kjartan.

628
00:47:18,240 --> 00:47:20,163
还记得他吗
Remember him?

629
00:47:21,000 --> 00:47:23,321
那个一定是斯文
And that must be Sven.

630
00:47:23,640 --> 00:47:25,608
不对劲，我们得去告诉拉格纳
This is wrong. We need to tell Ragnar.

631
00:47:25,760 --> 00:47:27,444
他们挡在我们和大厅之间
They're between us and the hall.

632
00:47:27,600 --> 00:47:31,366
那我们就绕路上去，把马留下，徒步跑过去
Then we go up and around. We leave the horses and run.

633
00:47:37,520 --> 00:47:40,330
就在门前，对，就这样
(KJARTAN) In front of the door. That's it.

634
00:47:49,680 --> 00:47:51,648
(DOG BARKING)

635
00:47:59,720 --> 00:48:02,371
拉格纳，有烟
(RAVN) Ragnar, smoke.

636
00:48:03,240 --> 00:48:05,481
着火了！蒂拉，快醒来！
Fire! Thyra, wake up!

637
00:48:05,640 --> 00:48:07,404
都醒醒！快起来！
All them! Wake up!

638
00:48:07,560 --> 00:48:09,688
着火了！
Fire!

639
00:48:10,600 --> 00:48:13,080


640
00:48:16,400 --> 00:48:17,890
快来 快点
(EARL RAGNAR) Come on! Come on!

641
00:48:18,040 --> 00:48:19,644
这边走 拉文
(SIGRID) This way. Ravn.

642
00:48:20,880 --> 00:48:23,565
- 救救我！- 来，快跟我来
(WOMAN) Help me! (SIGRID) Come. Come, quickly.

643
00:48:23,720 --> 00:48:25,290
快来
Come.

644
00:48:27,360 --> 00:48:29,886
- 这边门堵死了 - 这边也是
- The door is blocked. - So is this one.

645
00:48:33,720 --> 00:48:35,051
做好准备
Be ready.

646
00:48:35,240 --> 00:48:36,969


647
00:48:37,120 --> 00:48:40,522
这边开着！这边开着，跟我来
(MAN) This one's open! This one's open. Come on, follow me.

648
00:48:40,680 --> 00:48:42,250
这边走
(WOMAN) This way.

649
00:48:42,720 --> 00:48:44,529
抓住孩子们
(KJARTAN) Take the children.

650
00:48:47,960 --> 00:48:49,883
全抓走
Take them all.

651
00:48:50,080 --> 00:48:52,526


652
00:48:54,280 --> 00:48:55,611
弓箭手！
(KJARTAN) Archers!

653
00:48:56,000 --> 00:48:57,650
别上去，等我
Don't go up there. Wait for me.

654
00:48:57,800 --> 00:48:59,211
过来 过来
(SIGRID) Come. Come.

655
00:49:00,760 --> 00:49:03,366
- 啊！- 拉格纳
- Unh! - (SIGRID) Ragnar.

656
00:49:03,520 --> 00:49:06,842
关上门，蒂拉已经在我们手里了，其余的人就让他们烧死吧
Close the doors. We have Thyra. Let the rest burn.

657
00:49:11,800 --> 00:49:14,167

658
00:49:17,960 --> 00:49:19,928


659
00:50:04,080 --> 00:50:07,801
带她一同去英灵殿
Take her with you to Valhalla.

660
00:50:07,960 --> 00:50:10,531
好，我在那里等你
Yes. I will meet you there.

661
00:50:25,560 --> 00:50:28,928
啊！
Argh!

662
00:50:29,480 --> 00:50:33,007


663
00:50:41,760 --> 00:50:44,331


664
00:50:46,120 --> 00:50:47,690
不，不！
No. Oh, no.

665
00:50:50,440 --> 00:50:53,410


666
00:50:59,080 --> 00:51:00,764


667
00:51:04,760 --> 00:51:06,091


668
00:51:06,240 --> 00:51:07,730
找银子
Find the silver.

669
00:51:08,800 --> 00:51:10,131
快！
Now!

670
00:51:19,080 --> 00:51:21,686


671
00:51:22,160 --> 00:51:24,766
他们在搜拉格纳的财宝
They're searching for Ragnar's wealth.

672
00:51:26,480 --> 00:51:29,290
- 他们找不到的 - 去后面搜！
- They'll never find it. - (KJARTAN) Search in the back.

673
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:32,041
快点，我们马上就走
Come on, we're leaving soon.

674
00:51:34,440 --> 00:51:39,162
你以为我离开了你，还娶了别人
You thought I'd left you, marry someone else.

675
00:51:42,400 --> 00:51:45,131
但你知道
But do you know

676
00:51:45,760 --> 00:51:48,889
我要对这副身子做些什么吗？
what I will do with this body?

677
00:51:49,600 --> 00:51:52,922
对这张嘴？
This mouth?

678
00:51:57,760 --> 00:52:01,242
我要把所有梦里想过的事都做一遍
I will do all I have dreamt of

679
00:52:01,560 --> 00:52:03,244
还不止这些
and more.

680
00:52:03,400 --> 00:52:06,131
谁又能阻止我？
And who will call a halt?

681
00:52:08,120 --> 00:52:12,045
无畏伯爵拉格纳已死
Earl Ragnar the Fearless is gone.

682
00:52:12,480 --> 00:52:18,965
跟他一起的，还有乌特雷德，他那条撒克逊宠物
And with him, Uhtred, his Saxon pet,

683
00:52:19,120 --> 00:52:22,124
都化成灰了
a pile of ashes.

684
00:52:30,120 --> 00:52:31,724
随便你
Anything.

685
00:52:39,960 --> 00:52:45,046
- 嘘，蹲下 - 你看那个撒克逊人
- Shh. Get down. - Look at that man, the Saxon.

686
00:52:45,200 --> 00:52:47,521
他叫斯卡利昂，是我叔父的手下
His name's Scallion. He works with my uncle.

687
00:52:47,680 --> 00:52:50,684
- 他会去告诉叔父我已经死了 - 就让他去说吧
- He'll tell him that I'm dead. - Let him do it.

688
00:52:50,840 --> 00:52:53,650
- 我看见他和基尔坦在一起 - 把这里烧成灰
- I see him with Kjartan. - (KJARTAN) Burn it to the ground.

689
00:52:53,800 --> 00:52:55,564
也许他们在同流合污
(BRIDA) Maybe they're in it together.

690
00:52:55,720 --> 00:52:58,769
他们凭什么以为这么做不会受到惩罚?
And what makes them believe they can do this without punishment?

691
00:52:59,000 --> 00:53:02,209
嘘，他们会受到惩罚的，但不该出自你之手
Shh. They will be punished, but not by you.

692
00:53:02,360 --> 00:53:04,931
乌特雷德，听我说，活着才是对拉格纳最好的交代
Uhtred, listen to me, we serve Ragnar best alive.

693
00:53:05,080 --> 00:53:07,321
我们要把这件事说出去
We tell the story.

694
00:53:08,280 --> 00:53:10,726
- 我要杀人 - 不行
- I need to kill someone. - No.

695
00:53:10,880 --> 00:53:13,008
我选他
And I choose him.

696
00:53:15,040 --> 00:53:16,371
乌特雷德，不行
Uhtred, no.

697
00:53:17,840 --> 00:53:19,524
快点
(KJARTAN) Come on!

698
00:53:24,760 --> 00:53:26,091


699
00:53:29,760 --> 00:53:31,444


700
00:53:34,880 --> 00:53:38,043
最主要的事情是把马都聚在这儿
(KJARTAN) The main thing is to keep the horses together here.

701
00:53:39,000 --> 00:53:40,889
别把武器留在这里
Don't leave any weapons behind.

702
00:53:42,080 --> 00:53:45,004
把那些搬过去，去后面看看
Move those over and we'll look in the back.

703
00:53:45,160 --> 00:53:48,243
别留在里面，全都搬出来
Don't leave anything in there. Just bring it all out.

704
00:53:58,840 --> 00:54:00,683
再来一点
(KJARTAN) A little bit more.

705
00:54:14,720 --> 00:54:16,882
好 在这边！
(KJARTAN) Yeah. (MAN) Over here!

706
00:54:17,680 --> 00:54:19,284
嘿，快点
(KJARTAN) Hey, come on.

707
00:54:19,600 --> 00:54:21,523


708
00:54:26,920 --> 00:54:29,844
你知道我是谁吗?
Yeah. You know who I am?

709
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:33,482
你找的就是我
It's me you're looking for.

710
00:54:33,640 --> 00:54:36,371
你还记得我吗? 你还记得我吗?
You remember me? You remember me?

711
00:54:36,520 --> 00:54:38,284


712
00:54:38,440 --> 00:54:39,771


713
00:54:43,000 --> 00:54:44,843


714
00:54:58,480 --> 00:55:00,130
没有了
There's no more.

715
00:55:00,280 --> 00:55:01,611
- 我们走 - 快点
- We're going. - (SVEN) Come on.

716
00:55:02,320 --> 00:55:04,402
带上那些马
(KJARTAN) Bring the horses.

717
00:55:20,800 --> 00:55:23,451


718
00:55:49,520 --> 00:55:51,010


719
00:56:11,560 --> 00:56:14,484
按理说这些该归小拉格纳的
By right it belongs to young Ragnar.

720
00:56:14,880 --> 00:56:18,521
是的，但我们该花就花，先活下去
Yes. But we spend what we need to spend. We stay alive.

721
00:56:18,680 --> 00:56:21,411
我们把实情告诉他人，然后呢
We tell the story and then what?

722
00:56:24,560 --> 00:56:27,006
我们去投奔别的领主
We find a new lord to serve.

723
00:56:32,080 --> 00:56:36,130
我不会袖手旁观，让属于我的东西被人夺走
I will not stand by and have everything that's mine taken from me.

724
00:56:38,200 --> 00:56:40,009
我要回去
I'm going back.

725
00:56:40,160 --> 00:56:41,764
去哪儿
Where?

726
00:56:43,960 --> 00:56:46,042
回到起点
To the beginning.

727
00:57:32,560 --> 00:57:36,121


728
00:57:47,840 --> 00:57:49,808
- 是斯卡利昂吗？ - 不是，大人
- (AELFRIC) Is it Scallion? - No, my lord.

729
00:57:49,960 --> 00:57:53,681
- 他看起来像个丹麦人 - 可能是基尔坦的手下
- He looks like a Dane. - Could be one of Kjartan's men.

730
00:58:16,200 --> 00:58:19,010
我是贝班堡的乌特雷德，我要夺回属于我的一切！
I am Uhtred of Bebbanburg. I shall take what is mine!

731
00:58:21,640 --> 00:58:23,563
贝班堡是我的！
Bebbanburg's mine!

732
00:58:25,360 --> 00:58:27,283
备马
Horses.
